room_title: Escape room "Revenge of Atlantis" by EscapeTime in Annapolis
room_description: After a long journey to the middle of the Atlantic Ocean your expedition has finally reach the lost city of Atlantis. The journey has taken you deep in the waters of the Atlantic. Once inside you have angered the Sea God who has sealed off the exit. Your group has 60 minutes to find a way out with all the treasure.
